## Phase 3: Professor Detail Page

**Goal:** Build the full professor detail view with info editing, email drafting, and AI chat.

### Files

```
app/
  professor/
    [id]/
      page.tsx                            -- server component wrapper
components/
  professor/
    professor-info-panel.tsx              -- client: editable professor fields
    professor-info-form.tsx               -- client: form fields for professor
    email-draft-section.tsx               -- client: email drafting UI
    chat-section.tsx                      -- client: AI chat interface
    chat-message.tsx                      -- client: single chat bubble
    publication-list.tsx                  -- client: key publications display
    tag-input.tsx                         -- shared: tag/chip input for arrays
app/
  api/
    gemini/
      email/route.ts                     -- POST: generate email draft
      chat/route.ts                      -- POST: chat with professor context
      memory/route.ts                    -- POST: extract memory from chat
